moblin-keyboard-manager (0.51) gaston; urgency=low

  [ Jian Han ]
  * Create a configure file for each user
  * fix the issue that /usr/share/moblin-keyboard-mannager/menu.xml can only be written by root
    (using the copy in user's home)

  [ Bob Spencer ]
  * Added some size (52x52) for the button, but it doesn't seem to help
  * Changed the icon to have transparent background so statusbar theme shows

  [ Horace Li ]
  * Implement a new method to spawn and terminate virutal keyboard.
  * Remove menu.xml as we are attempting to store layout information as well
    as others by gconf.
  * Clean up code, fix warnings.
  * Rename libkeyboard.png to mp_keyboard.png and install it to /usr/share/icons.
  * Following freedesktop instructions on attaching icon to GtkButton.
  * Update the icon png to our new one drawed by Jason, and rename the icon to vkeyboard,
    installing to 24x24 to match GTK_ICON size.
  * Read layout option from gconf path.
  * Reset "layout" default value and set the auto_launch key as a boolean value.
  * Cut a new release.

